{"tid":2255914,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過腰椎間盤突出？","createTime":"2020-10-24T03:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T05:07:50.000Z","uid":160159,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"83f41c7bbd0221f43c28d8e9094d4539513b56ce","tid":2255914,"uid":160159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T03:08:20.000Z","msg":"最近因為搬野整親條腰<br />\n開頭諗住只係拉親，但過咗一個星期隻腳開始都痺痛<br />\n所以去左睇骨科照mrl，證實L4/5突出<br />\nSofar做左7次物理治療，但好似都冇乜改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n腳仲痺仲易攰左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下有冇巴打可以分享下<br />\n要做幾耐先會好？同埋中醫針灸推拿會唔會好啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a2d8cd5d9940e55652d2dbc54b4d01a7acc0ed","tid":2255914,"uid":120093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T03:12:47.000Z","msg":"我睇左脊醫中醫針灸都唔得 情況越來越差 床都落唔到了"},{"pid":"7a09d29cb5ffc76f1644c4cf8c1045f3471b63ef","tid":2255914,"uid":292455,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T03:13:31.000Z","msg":"試下訓硬啲既床，有啲拉筋動作可以舒緩，記得注意坐姿 呢個好重要，坐時背部下半要有倚靠"},{"pid":"ac2fac38ec020dcdbeabb115c87c3391245a11cd","tid":2255914,"uid":151955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T03:14:37.000Z","msg":"好多人都有，我都有好耐，不過唔嚴重，只係出小小<br />\n醫生有無咩建議比你，例如做手術？<br />\n平時做下輕量運動，游下水咁，千祈唔好快，強化番周邊肌肉會好啲，跑步都唔係咁好。"},{"pid":"51377e37523beecaadff43a33a3cc9af362fc69e","tid":2255914,"uid":112845,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T03:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24e93ce3ff2f9b023e5131539fb6e885b34fccc1","tid":2255914,"uid":303530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T03:16:28.000Z","msg":"屋企老人家8X歲 早幾年整親椎間盤突出<br />\n又唔敢做手術，睇骨科同脊醫都唔得<br />\n最後係搵左個中醫教授同物理治療師雙管齊下搞左半年，好在最後無事好得返"},{"pid":"4c94b51642a2c6ba7caf55b2405519bafa642b3c","tid":2255914,"u