itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T03:34:38.000Z","msg":"咁又冇，我知去到呢啲情況一定要做手術啦"},{"pid":"a97f03e8f124eb1b950d6527d9794dceb9301269","tid":2255914,"uid":299467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T03:34:52.000Z","msg":"lm學野，我都有椎間盤突出，細個睇過脊醫，經絡治療，有好番d<br />\n但都好似樓上巴打咁，耐唔耐轉天氣個陣又會痛番，之前會去睇物理治療既，但淨係做下機，<br />\n所以呢排試緊睇跌打，幫我按下好似舒服d咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得最緊要都係平時要拉筋，唔好寒背，一懶又痛番"},{"pid":"2aeccf9727bc756c30bf1f462eb17b32387e2a97","tid":2255914,"uid":160159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6ddf8a62f51bbb6d968c62cd035ebedbf8457c7","tid":2255914,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83f41c7bbd0221f43c28d8e9094d4539513b56ce","tid":2255914,"uid":160159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T03:08:20.000Z","msg":"最近因為搬野整親條腰<br />\n開頭諗住只係拉親，但過咗一個星期隻腳開始都痺痛<br />\n所以去左睇骨科照mrl，證實L4/5突出<br />\nSofar做左7次物理治療，但好似都冇乜改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n腳仲痺仲易攰左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下有冇巴打可以分享下<br />\n要做幾耐先會好？同埋中醫針灸推拿會唔會好啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T03:24:59.000Z","msg":"恩霖中醫診所 地址：九龍彌敦道491-493號展望大廈7／F,491A室 油麻地地鐵站c出口 電話：23873404 診症時間： 上午10：00-下午2：00 下午4：00-晚上8：00 星期日、公眾假期休息<br />\n<br />\n利申：曾有小歪，睇好過，有人痛到企唔直都可以睇得好<br />\n缺點： 貴"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T03:36:14.000Z","msg":"巴打係骨歪左？一次幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d9c1b8bbff087b38c715d03ebbd0e095e978d9","tid":2255914,"uid":160159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b388b3bf561bf016244562185c2670ec65401ef3","tid":2255914,"uid":134095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83f41c7bbd0221f43c28d8e9094d4539513b56ce","tid":2255914,"uid":160159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T03:08:20.0